          { question: "Can the taxi boot carry bottles?", answer: "Yes, our sedan holds 2-3 cases (12-18 bottles). For larger quantities or fragile vintage bottles, choose our Van." },
          { question: "Is there a direct train Bordeaux — Cognac?", answer: "No, there is no regular direct rail service. A taxi is the most practical and fastest solution (1h20 vs 2h+ by train with connection)." },
          { question: "Can the taxi bring me back after tastings?", answer: "Absolutely! It is one of the main advantages of a taxi for visiting Cognac. Your driver waits or returns to collect you at the agreed time." }
