          { question: "Is Marmande on the Bordeaux-Toulouse TER line?", answer: "Yes, Marmande is on the Bordeaux–Agen–Toulouse TER line. 6-8 trains/day, 55 min from Bordeaux. The station is a 10-minute walk from the town centre." }
